title: Former Union Finance Minister Yashwant Sinha predicts BJP will lose in western Uttar Pradesh - The New Indian Express
content: Former Union Finance Minister Yashwant Sinha predicts BJP will lose in western Uttar Pradesh  The New Indian Express
description: Former Union FM Yashwant Sinha claimed that BJP would not get more than 20 seats out of 58 in the first phase of polling in Western UP.
